acceptance

Interface AcceptanceOmega

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AcceptanceBuchi, AcceptanceGeneric, AcceptanceGenRabin, AcceptanceRabin, AcceptanceReach, AcceptanceStreett

    public interface AcceptanceOmega
extends java.lang.Cloneable
    Generic interface for an omega-regular acceptance condition (BitSet-based).

        AcceptanceOmega complement(int numStates,
                           AcceptanceType... allowedAcceptance)
                    throws PrismException
        Complement the acceptance condition if possible.
        Parameters:
        numStates - the number of states in the underlying model / automaton (needed for complementing BitSets)
        allowedAcceptance - the allowed acceptance types that may be used for complementing
        Throws:
        PrismException

      • lift

        void lift(AcceptanceOmega.LiftBitSet lifter)
        Lift the state sets in the acceptance condition. For each state set states in the condition, lifter.lift(states) is called and the state set is replaced by the result.
